          <td>
            <table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <h1 style="text-align:center">Research Data Stewards Newsletter</h1>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="text-align:center">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <h1>Launch of the Research Cockpit</h1><img src="https://ms.copernica.com/API/base/copernica/imagedata?id=222638141&amp;hashcode=69c8b621460042cf7a1330ee508e3b7b&amp;_language=nl_NL&amp;_timezone=Europe%2FAmsterdam&amp;_account=7713&amp;_user=864064" style="display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" width="100%" />
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0">We are pleased to announce the launch of the Research Cockpit, a new system designed to assist researchers in managing their research data. This platform will evolve gradually, with additional products and services being introduced over time to support the entire research data lifecycle.</p><a href="https://tue.atlassian.net/helpcenter/research/" style="background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:0.375rem;padding-top:0.75rem;padding-bottom:0.75rem;padding-left:1rem;padding-right:1rem;text-align:center;font-weight:600;width:100%;margin-top:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:100%;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;mso-padding-alt:0px;padding:12px 16px 12px 16px" target="_blank"><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:400%;mso-text-raise:18" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;</i><![endif]--></span><span style="max-width:100%;display:inline-block;line-height:120%;mso-padding-alt:0px;mso-text-raise:9px">Go to the Research Cockpit</span><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:400%" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8203;</i><![endif]--></span></a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <h2>Meet your data stewards</h2>
                    <table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation">
                      <tbody style="width:100%">
                        <tr style="width:100%">
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/liz-guzman-ramirez" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/E6F3DA4B/0800161685d9da5130b9511cba31c392/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/liz-guzman-ramirez" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Liz Guzman-Ramirez</a><br />Team Lead</p>
                          </td>
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/angela-aleksovska" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/BB3A9314/ee39d529ae257a6908e3758531571254/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/angela-aleksovska" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Angela Aleksovska</a><br />EE</p>
                          </td>
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/davide-nardi" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/E82F130D/fa32dc3e0d3441ce1852d33fb8d51e19/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/davide-nardi" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Davide Nardi</a><br />M&amp;CS</p>
                          </td>
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/jayakrishnan-harikrishnavilas-raveendran-nair" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/BB86F741/93d2bfd61ff25a0a39b32e1676291921/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/jayakrishnan-harikrishnavilas-raveendran-nair" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Jay Nair</a><br />IE&amp;IS</p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation">
                      <tbody style="width:100%">
                        <tr style="width:100%">
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/lucia-forrov%C3%A1" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/971233E4/457149811614201b7c24d74f26fda13f/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/lucia-forrov%C3%A1" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Lucia Forrová</a><br />BE</p>
                          </td>
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/neda-norouzi" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/0975110E/8d60fc12cda6126569fccb399b7e47d4/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/neda-norouzi" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Neda Nozouri</a><br />BmE, ME</p>
                          </td>
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/mariana-oshima-menegon" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/85AFDEB0/f81afc1780baf6f860eadf403b8bdf33/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/mariana-oshima-menegon" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Mariana Oshima Menegon</a><br />ID</p>
                          </td>
                          <td data-id="__react-email-column" style="width:25%;padding-left:0.5rem;padding-right:0.5rem;vertical-align:top"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/nami-sunami" style="color:#067df7;text-decoration:none" target="_blank"><img height="150" src="https://tracking.tue.nl/pic/acc/7713/A633B04A/1eea2ae7c4fb325dafcbfc26b0666199/image.png" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:0.5rem;display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none" /></a>
                            <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0"><a href="https://research.tue.nl/en/persons/nami-sunami" style="font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration:none" target="_blank">Nami Sunami</a><br />CE&amp;C, APSE</p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
